# ğŸ“ College Project Access Portal - Backend

This is the backend for a College Project Portal developed using *Node.js, **Express.js, and **MongoDB Atlas*.  
It allows students to:
- View project details
- Verify their identity using student ID cards via OCR
- Securely access project data based on college affiliation

